	  <part id="mcp">
	    <title>Model Context Protocol (MCP)</title>
	    <slide id="mcp">
	      <title>Model Context Protocol (MCP)</title>
	      <img src="mcp-logo.png" style="float: right ; width : 20% ; margin : 0% 4% 4% 4% ; "/>
	      <ul>
	        <li>MCP seems to be the new <q>standard protocol</q> for LLM consumers</li>
	        <li>Many mapping tools generate MCP from OpenAPI descriptions</li>
	        <li>Problem #1: Complex APIs will overload the MCP host's context</li>
	        <li>Problem #2: Larger API landscapes will overload the MCP host's context</li>
	        <li>Problem #3: Bad AX results in unsatisfactory AI results</li>
	      </ul>
